  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    World anti-corruption day newsletter: December 2020
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Provides a progress update on the government's efforts to battle corruption both in the UK and abroad.</p>

  </div>
</div>

